  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149880/extras/efacf586d1ee3f2e3035b461c9094292.poster.avif?t=1665140094\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149880/extras/efacf586d1ee3f2e3035b461c9094292.webm?t=1665140094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149880/extras/efacf586d1ee3f2e3035b461c9094292.mp4?t=1665140094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Defend your base classroom using a large variety of <strong>towers</strong>, <strong>upgrades</strong> and <strong>effects</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149880/extras/7b2aeb95916fc8ebb13466d4939a2563.avif?t=1665140094\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>With over 80 different cards there are plenty of possibilities and every run will be different from the last.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149880/extras/e9d76cd81ed17dffecd51d4851411a9c.avif?t=1665140094\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>Gain <strong>star stickers</strong> after defeating bosses that can be used to unlock permanent bonuses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149880/extras/3e96ef3900de209ead92bf5448d46abe.avif?t=1665140094\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br>The hallway extensions are random each game so be ready to adapt to different situations!",
